Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: hda - reduce msleep time if EPSS power states supported
Git-commit: 0f4ccbb02533276ab750961e150aeee06492ed7c
Patch-mainline: 3.6-rc1
References: bnc#801713

if EPSS supported, transition from D3 state to D0 state in less
than 10ms

Signed-off-by: Wang Xingchao <xingchao.wang@intel.com>
Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

